          <title>Los Angeles sheriff's department to retest 4,000 DNA samples after using faulty kits for 8 months</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LOS ANGELES (AP) — The Los Angeles County Sheriff’s Department said this week it will retest 4,000 DNA samples and open an internal investigation after learning that it used potentially flawed test kits for eight months.]]></description>
